Task:
In this challenge, you will be given 2 integers,n and m . There are n words, which might repeat, in word group A. There are m words
belonging to word group B. For each m words, check whether the word has appeared in group A or not. Print the indices of each occurrence
of m in group A. If it does not appear, print -1.
Program:
rom collections import defaultdict
n,m=map(int,input().split())
group_indices=defaultdict(list)
for i in range(1,n+1):
    word=input().strip()
    group_indices[word].append(str(i))
for word in range(m):
    word=input().strip()
    if word in group_indices:
        print(" ".join(group_indices[word]))
    else:
        print("-1")
